  "instructions": [
    "Peel and julienne the celeriac, carrot, and cucumber, and place them in a large bowl.",
    "Finely slice the red chili and add it to the bowl with the vegetables.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together lime juice, soy sauce, crushed garlic, a pinch of salt, and toasted sesame seeds.",
    "Pour the dressing over the vegetables and toss gently until evenly coated.",
    "Sprinkle toasted coconut flakes, chopped cilantro, and toasted coriander seeds over the salad.",
    "Let the salad rest for 5 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Serve the salad warm or at room temperature as a light lunch.",
    "Garnish with an extra sprinkle of sesame seeds before serving."
